## 1. WHY THE HERO‚ÄôS JOURNEY MATTERS TO PANTHEONOS

The Hero‚Äôs Journey (Campbell/Vogler) is the world‚Äôs most stable symbolic state machine of human transformation.

PantheonOS integrates it not as literature, but as **architecture** because:
* It compresses massive psychological complexity into a predictable structure.
* It maps cleanly onto AAE bearings (Thesis‚ÄìAntithesis‚ÄìSynthesis).
* Zero-type transformations correspond directly to stage transitions.
* It makes human development computationally legible for AI reasoning sequences.

